title: LabJal.Offline. Loader [Nextel,Boost Mobile]
description:
This program is used for transferring Ringtones, Wallpapers, Java Applications & Games onto your Nextel, Boost Mobile and Motorola iDEN phones. Very similar to the versions of MyJAL and WebJAL This is an OFFLINE Loader so there is no need to be online while using this program. This program also lets you view files that are 
already stored on the phone. Use at your own risk. Use of this program or any other loader are known to damage phones when incorrect data cables are used. Make sure the phones battery is fully charged since power loss during transfers damage the phones memory. Back-Up your phones entire information and data before the use of the program. You have been warned!!!  This software is compatible with most Nextel &
Boost Mobile phones (i285,i415,i455,i710,i730,i835,i860,i870,,etc,,) provided you
have the correct USB/SERIAL Cable. Enclosed is also a copy of the USB Driver which should be installed also. If you need any help with ringtones,wallpapers,games or even installing this program and getting it to work can be found on google.com. Just SEARCH!!
